&lt;a href="https://pkg.garrickadenbuie.com/xaringanExtra/#/panelset" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://pkg.garrickadenbuie.com/xaringanExtra/#/panelset&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>For example, this panelset:&lt;/p>
&lt;div id="" class="panelset">
 
&lt;div class="panel">
 &lt;div class="panel-name">Hello! üëã&lt;/div>
 
 &lt;p>hello&lt;/p>
&lt;/div>
&lt;div class="panel">
 &lt;div class="panel-name">Goodbye üí®&lt;/div>
 
 &lt;p>goodbye&lt;/p>
&lt;/div>

&lt;/div>
&lt;p>Was created by combining this theme&amp;rsquo;s &lt;code>panelset&lt;/code> and &lt;code>panel&lt;/code> shortcodes:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="background-color:#fff;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-go" data-lang="go">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#1f2328">{{&amp;lt;&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#1f2328">panelset&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#1f2328">class&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#1f2328">=&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#0a3069">&amp;#34;greetings&amp;#34;&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#1f2328">&amp;gt;}}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#1f2328">{{&amp;lt;&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#1f2328">panel&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#1f2328">name&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#1f2328">=&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#0a3069">&amp;#34;Hello! :wave:&amp;#34;&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#1f2328">&amp;gt;}}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#1f2328">hello&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#1f2328">{{&amp;lt;&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#0550ae">/&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#1f2328">panel&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#1f2328">&amp;gt;}}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#1f2328">{{&amp;lt;&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#1f2328">panel&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#1f2328">name&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#1f2328">=&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#0a3069">&amp;#34;Goodbye :dash:&amp;#34;&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#1f2328">&amp;gt;}}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#1f2328">goodbye&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#1f2328">{{&amp;lt;&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#0550ae">/&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#1f2328">panel&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#1f2328">&amp;gt;}}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#1f2328">{{&amp;lt;&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#0550ae">/&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#1f2328">panelset&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#1f2328">&amp;gt;}}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>You could also revert to HTML as well. For example, this panelset:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="panelset">
 &lt;div class="panel">
 &lt;div class="panel-name">Question&lt;/div>
 &lt;!-- Panel content -->
 &lt;p>Which came first: the :chicken: or the :egg:?&lt;/p>
 &lt;/div>
 &lt;div class="panel">
 &lt;div class="panel-name">Answer :hatching_chick:&lt;/div>
 &lt;!-- Panel content -->
 &lt;p>Team :egg: FTW!&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>An Rmarkdown post</title><link>https://jlumbroso.github.io/hugo-apero-github-template/blog/rmarkdown/</link><pubDate>Wed, 30 Dec 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://jlumbroso.github.io/hugo-apero-github-template/blog/rmarkdown/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="air-quality">Air quality
